<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lien invalide — SailingLoc</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7fb; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        .card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); max-width: 480px; width: 100%; margin: 24px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background-color: #0a4d8c; padding: 32px 40px; }
        .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .body { padding: 48px 40px 40px; }
        .icon { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        h2 { color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 22px; }
        p { color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 32px; font-size: 15px; }
        .footer { padding: 20px 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>⚓ SailingLoc</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
        <div class="icon">❌</div>
        <h2>Lien invalide ou expiré</h2>
        <p>Ce lien de confirmation n'est pas valide ou a déjà été utilisé.<br>Si vous avez besoin d'aide, contactez le support SailingLoc.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} SailingLoc — Tous droits réservés
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
